{"tid":1166896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【40℃熱爆】農地粟米變爆谷！ 雲南高溫缺雨「乾燒」","createTime":"2019-05-22T17:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T00:24:50.000Z","uid":231886,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9d547bd08bca20a60a5e640cfd3ff2a5e39710","tid":1166896,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:13:43.000Z","msg":"雲南昨日出現高溫天氣，農田中的粟米竟變成爆谷！當地氣象台昨日上午10時發佈24小時高溫黃色預警，其中金沙江河谷、元江河谷及瀾滄江河谷地區最高氣溫將達到35℃以上，而元陽、元江甚至超過40℃。昆明廣播電視台在微信公眾號貼出相片，指在雲南元江的農田中，粟米被曬到「自爆」，變成爆谷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據悉，自今年4月以來，雲南全省平均氣溫為20.8℃，較常年同期偏高1.9℃，更是1961年以來溫度最高的一年。其中曲靖西部、昆明、文山西部、紅河、玉溪大部、楚雄大部和西雙版納北部等地區，氣溫甚至比往年高出2至4℃。而全省平均日照時數為349.3小時，較常年同期偏多9.9%。<br />\n另外，4月以來全省平均降雨量僅35.3毫米，較常年少了61.2%，為1961年以來降雨量第2少的年份；其中，滇中地區累積降雨更不足10毫米。當局預計，這種高溫乾旱天氣，將持續在雲南全省大部份地區出現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkD3kst.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkD3kst.jpg&h=cb823d60&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190520/59622240?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1Llwd_ckpd1gFM9enPIqCjqkQf4xSOKML0rkgj7ppEL_QxCwrYzD0zvSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59622240%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1Llwd_ckpd1gFM9enPIqCjqkQf4xSOKML0rkgj7ppEL_QxCwrYzD0zvSw&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSwgLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=9f12b55a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59622240%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1Llwd_ckpd1gFM9enPIqCjqkQf4xSOKML0rkgj7ppEL_QxCwrYzD0zvSw&h=dff55c9b\" data-auto-link targ